compareParameters.CP_TABLE_LIST_QUERY: SELECT table_schema, table_name, Str_to_date(Date_format(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(), '%Y-%m-%d %H:00:00'), '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i:%s') AS LOG_CREATED_ON, COALESCE(has_created_on_col, 0) AS HAS_CREATED_ON_COL FROM information_schema.tables t LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT table_name AS table_col, CASE WHEN Count(*) > 0 THEN '1' ELSE '0' END AS has_created_on_col FROM information_schema.columns WHERE Upper(column_name) = 'CREATED_ON' GROUP BY table_name) c ON t.table_name = c.table_col WHERE ( table_schema LIKE 'mars-consumer-%' OR table_schema LIKE 'mars-contact-record-%' OR table_schema LIKE 'mars-contacts-%' OR table_schema LIKE 'mars-task-%' OR table_schema LIKE 'task-%' OR table_schema LIKE 'mars-ecms-%' OR table_schema LIKE 'mars-enrollment%' OR table_schema LIKE 'mars-blats%' OR table_schema LIKE 'mars-plan-provider%' OR table_schema LIKE 'mars-tenant-manager' OR table_schema LIKE 'mars-cti%' OR (table_schema LIKE 'mars-etl%' AND table_name LIKE 'ETL_REPORT%')) AND table_schema NOT LIKE 'mars-blats1-camunda%' AND table_schema NOT LIKE 'mars-consumer-v2%' AND table_name NOT LIKE 'AUDIT_LOG' AND table_name NOT LIKE 'GRID' AND table_name NOT LIKE 'GRID_COLUMNS' AND table_name NOT LIKE 'GRID_COLUMN_PROPERTIES' AND table_name NOT LIKE 'SECTION' AND table_name NOT LIKE 'UI_PERMISSIONS' AND table_name NOT LIKE 'PAGE' AND table_name NOT LIKE 'PORTFOLIO' AND table_name NOT LIKE 'PRIVACY_NOTICE' AND table_name NOT LIKE 'flyway_schema_history' AND table_name NOT LIKE 'USER_SECURITY' AND table_name NOT LIKE 'CASELOADER_PAYLOAD' AND Concat(table_schema, table_name) NOT LIKE 'mars-consumer-%CONSUMER_AUTHENTICATION' AND Concat(table_schema, table_name) NOT LIKE '%task%EXTERNAL_REQ_RESPONSE' AND table_name NOT LIKE 'caseloader_payload' AND table_name NOT LIKE '%_DEL_%' AND table_name NOT LIKE 'EVENT_SUBSCRIBER_RECORD' AND table_name NOT LIKE 'PROJECT_ROLE_API_ACCESS' AND table_name NOT LIKE 'ADDRESS_TRANSACTION' AND table_name NOT LIKE 'CONSUMER_TRANSACTION' AND table_name NOT LIKE 'CASE_CONSUMER_TRANSACTION' AND table_name NOT LIKE 'PHONE_TRANSACTION' AND table_name NOT LIKE 'EMAIL_TRANSACTION' AND table_name NOT LIKE 'CONSUMER_PROCESS_STAGING' -- and table_rows > 0 order by 2 desc;

extractionParameters.INCLUDE_TABLES: mars-consumer-%.%, mars-contact-record-%.%, mars-contacts-%.%, mars-task-%.%, mars-ecms-%.%, mars-enrollment%.%, mars-blats%.%, mars-plan-provider%.%, mars-event%.%, mars-tenant-manager.%,task-%.%
extractionParameters.IGNORE_TABLES: mars-consumer-v2%.%,mars-cti-%.%, mars-etl-%.%, mars-bpm%.%, mars-rules.%, mars-blats1-camunda%.%, mars-tm-config.%, mars-%.%_TRANSACTION, mars-%.AUDIT_LOG, mars-%.DATE_FIELD, mars-%.DISPLAY_LABEL, mars-%.GRID, mars-%.GRID_COLUMNS, mars-%.GRID_COLUMN_PROPERTIES, mars-%.SECTION, mars-%.TASK_TEMPLATE_TYPE_MAP, mars-%.UI_PERMISSIONS, mars-%.FIELDS, mars-%.PAGE, mars-%.USER_ACTIVITY_DETAILS, mars-%.TASK_SEARCH, mars-%.PROJECT_CONFIGURATIONS, mars-%.CASELOADER_PAYLOAD, mars-%.PORTFOLIO, mars-%.PRIVACY_NOTICE, mars-%.TASK_QUEUE_FILTER, mars-%.TASK_QUEUE_FILTER_SCOPE, mars-%.TASK_QUEUE_FILTER_TASK_TYPES, mars-%.TASK_FIELD, mars-%.TASK_TEMPLATE, mars-%.TASK_TEMPLATE_FIELD, mars-%.TASK_TYPE_PERMISSION, mars-%.FIELD_VALIDATION, mars-%.USER_SECURITY, mars-%.flyway_schema_history, mars-%.HOLIDAY_HISTORY, mars-%.CONTACT_RECORD_EDIT_HISTORY, mars-consumer-%.CONSUMER_AUTHENTICATION, mars-%.EXTERNAL_REQ_RESPONSE, mars-%.TRANSACTIONS, mars-%.USER_SECURITY, mars-%.BUSINESS_DAYS, mars-%.BUSINESS_DAYS_HISTORY, mars-%.%BKP% ,mars-%.%_TEMP_%, mars-%.%_TEMP, mars-contact-record-%.CALL_DATA, mars-contact-record-%.CTI_ENTITY, mars-contact-record-%.META_DATA
